# Deep Rock Galactic, with Flydigi Apex 2 in mind
mousecalibration 4200
flicktime 200
ingamemouse 2.5

CamXY mouse 100
ActionWheelXY flick # Flick with wheel
mousepriority flick # Disable normal camera motion while using wheel
flickdeadzone 40

# Unmap everything Rigth Stick and X Button

# Seperate reload and interact buttons (disable ActionH button with steam input)
ActionR R # Reload / Alt-Fire
ActionH E # Interact

ActionC !! A , D # Escape Freeze
ActionD V # ROCK AND STONE
